<bibRefCitation author="Dubatolov" box="[389,723,152,178]" pageId="3" pageNumber="580" refString="Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Haynes, P. G. (2008) Reviewing the African tiger-moth genera. 1. New genera from the late Prof. V. S. Murzin's collection (Lepidoptera, Arctiidae). Atalanta, 39 (1 / 4), 356 - 366, [col. pl. 15.]" type="book chapter" year="2008">Dubatolov et Haynes, 2008</bibRefCitation>
